%2C%20Deputy%20CM%20D%20K%20Shivakumar%20and%20other%20Congress%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20Wednesday%20expelled%20Yatnal%20from%20the%20primary%20membership%20of%20the%20party%20for%20six%20years%2C%20for%20repeated%20violation%20of%20the%20party%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20strongly%20advocate%20Hindutva%20are%20being%20suppressed%20in%20the%20party%20because%20of%20the%20selfishness%20of%20Yediyurappa's%20son%2C%20today%20even%20I'm%20suppressed%20because%20of%20the%20persistence%20of%20Vijayendra%20and%20Yediyurappa%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20their%20dynastic%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Yatnal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20here%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20still%20requests%20the%20party%20high%20command%20which%20is%20against%20the%20dynasty%20politics%20and%20corruption%2C%20that%20if%20they%20don't%20remove%20those%20indulging%20in%20adjustment%20politics%2C%20people%20of%20the%20state%20will%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20high%20command%20decides%20to%20continue%20Vijayendra%20for%20the%20next%20term%20(as%20president)%20and%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20for%20the%20next%20assembly%20polls%2C%20a%20time%20will%20come%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20to%20take%20a%20strong%20decision%20for%20a%20new%20future%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20state%2C%20with%20people%20who%20are%20honest%2C%20not%20corrupt%20and%20those%20who%20protect%20Sanatana%20dharma%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20PM%20Modi%20repeatedly%20states%20in%20his%20speeches%20that%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20dynasty%20and%20adjustment%20politics%20and%20corruption%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20Yatnal%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3Bthen%20why%20is%20Vijayendra%20still%20there%3F%20Vijayendra%20is%20corrupt%20and%20it%20is%20because%20of%20him%20Yediyurappa%20went%20to%20jail%3B%20There%20are%20allegations%20of%20forgery%20against%20him%3B%20his%20name%20is%20behind%20PSI%20and%2040%20per%20cent%20commission%20scam.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20party%20wants%20to%20continue%20with%20a%20family%20that%20is%20involved%20in%20several%20scams%2C%20the%20Hindus%20and%20Hindu%20karyakartas%20of%20this%20state%20will%20have%20to%20take%20a%20decision.%20We%20will%20start%20an%20awareness%20in%20this%20regard%20from%20today%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20suggesting%20building%20a%20new%20%26quot%3BHindu%20party%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20BJP%20couldn't%20protect%20Hindus%20now%20he%20said%20and%20cited%20instances%20of%20alleged%20attack%20on%20Hindu%20Karyakartas%20when%20Yediyurappa%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20is%20a%20Muslim%20party%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20speak%20about%20them%2C%20if%20BJP%20doesn't%20become%20Hindu%20party%2C%20the%20people%20of%20this%20state%20will%20make%20a%20historic%20decision.%20If%20you%20(BJP%20high%20command)%20give%20responsibility%20(of%20BJP)%20to%20Yediyurppa%20family%20BJP%20will%20face%20a%20humiliating%20defeat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20he%20also%20accused%20Yediyurappa%20of%20betraying%20north%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20it%20clear%20that%20his%20fight%20was%20not%20against%20the%20BJP%20or%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Yatnal%20said%2C%20that%20if%20the%20country%20is%20secure%20today%20it%20is%20because%20of%20Modi%20he%20urged%20the%20party%20to%20give%20the%20state%20leadership%20to%20someone%20who%20is%20honest%20like%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20the%20party%20leadership%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20feeling%20that%20there%20is%20no%20one%20else%20other%20than%20Yediyurappa%20and%20his%20family%20and%20that%20the%20dominant%20Veerashaiva-Lingayat%20community%20will%20go%20away%20from%20the%20party%20if%20the%20party%20decides%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20he%20and%20his%20associates%20will%20get%20a%20survey%20done%20and%20gather%20public%20opinion%20regarding%20the%20need%20for%20a%20party%20that%20will%20protect%20the%20Sanatana%20Hindu%20dharma%20that%20is%20pro%20development%20--%20especially%20north%20Karnataka--%20Yatnal%20said%20the%20people%20have%20already%20come%20forward%20to%20give%20donations%20for%20the%20new%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20abide%20by%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20people.%20We%20are%20not%20finding%20a%20future%20here%20(in%20BJP).%20Yediyurappa%20family%20is%20conspiring%20to%20sideline%20Hindu%20leaders.%20If%20the%20people%20opine%20in%20favour%20of%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20party%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20on%20Vijayadashami%2C%20we%20will%20hundred%20per%20cent%20launch%20a%20new%20political%20setup%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20he%20had%20not%20indulged%20in%20any%20act%20of%20indiscipline%20while%20asking%20for%20proof%20of%20his%20indiscipline%2C%20the%20grounds%20on%20which%20he%20was%20expelled%2C%20Yatnal%20said%2C%20he%20never%20criticized%20BJP%20or%20Modi%20or%20party's%20ideology%20and%20never%20voted%20against%20the%20party's%20official%20candidate%2C%20nor%20had%20attended%20any%20Congress%20or%20JD(S)%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20anti-BJP%2C%20I'm%20anti-Yediyurappa%20as%20Yediyurappa%20has%20betrayed%20the%20people%20of%20north%20Karnataka%2C%20he%20suppressed%20many%20including%20me%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20his%20son.%20I%20still%20regard%20BJP%20like%20my%20mother%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYatnal%20also%20claimed%20that%20Vijayendra%20and%20his%20supporters%20are%20worried%20about%20the%20latter%20being%20removed%20from%20the%20president%20post%2C%20following%20his%20expulsion.%20%26quot%3BThey%20fear%20what%20if%20the%20high%20command%20decides%20for%20a%20tie%2C%20by%20taking%20action%20against%20Vijayendra%20too%2C%20after%20my%20expulsion.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%