band's%20probable%20thought%20process%20because%20understanding%20what%20someone%20is%20thinking%20is%20essential%20to%20figuring%20out%20what%20to%20do%20about%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%2C%20I%20had%20a%20friend%20who%20lived%20in%20town%3B%20neither%20she%20nor%20her%20partner%20had%20outdoorsy%20hobbies%20or%20vocations%20that%20called%20for%20much%20hauling%2C%20and%20yet%20her%20husband%20was%20insistent%20that%20a%20pricey%20pickup%20truck%20was%20the%20most%20financially%20sound%20vehicle%20purchase%20they%20could%20make.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERather%20than%20just%20admitting%20he%20liked%20trucks%20and%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20cool%20to%20own%20one%2C%20he%20explained%20how%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fbest-cheap-car-insurance-companies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echeap%20car%20insurance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20premiums%20would%20offset%20the%20higher%20gas%20costs.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20more%20affordable%20car%20would%20be%20so%20dangerous%20and%20expensive%20in%20the%20long%20term%20that%20he%20refused%20to%20consider%20it.%20The%20best%20part%20of%20his%20pitch%20was%20that%20he%20believed%20it.%20Somehow%2C%20this%20man%20had%20convinced%20himself%20that%20he%20couldn't%20sleep%20at%20night%20with%20a%20sensible%20four-door%20sedan%20in%20the%20garage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20tell%20this%20story%20to%20explain%20why%20your%20best%20bet%20isn't%20arguing%20the%20merits%20of%20your%20desires%20or%20pleading%20for%20fairness.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EPointing%20out%20the%20double%20standard%20to%20him%20is%20unlikely%20to%20blow%20your%20husband's%20mind%20and%20immediately%20change%20his%20entire%20worldview.%3Cspan%3E%20Instead%2C%20I%20suggest%20you%20step%20into%20your%20power%20as%20an%20equal%20in%20this%20marriage%20and%20stop%20asking%20for%20permission.%20Rearranging%20your%20fi