-living-in-melbourne-cons-made-me-leave-australia-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emoved%20from%20Melbourne%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Bright%2C%20Australia.%20We'd%20lived%20in%20Melbourne%20for%20eight%20years%20and%20were%20ready%20for%20a%20change.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20night%20in%20October%202021%2C%20my%20husband%20put%20an%20idea%20on%20the%20table.%20He%20asked%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20turn%20over%20a%20new%20leaf%20and%20move%20to%20Bright%2C%20where%20his%20family%20was%20based.%20We'd%20already%20vacationed%20there%20plenty%20of%20times%2C%20and%20I'd%20enjoyed%20it%2C%20so%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSure%2C%20let's%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%20Soon%2C%20we%20were%20planning%20our%20escape%20from%20Melbourne.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257339dd2-1c24-4b5e-9a1e-aa03511454a2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20decided%20not%20to%20sell%20our%20home%20in%20Melbourne%20when%20we%20moved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe'd%20been%20living%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funmarried-couples-buying-house-lawyer-advice-split-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehome%20we'd%20bought%20together%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20four%20years%2C%20and%20though%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20leave%20Melbourne%2C%20I%20had%20reservations%20about%20selling.%20We%20also%20didn't%20want%20to%20buy%20in%20Bright%20because%20I%20didn't%20know%20whether%20I'd%20enjoy%20living%20in%20such%20a%20small%20town.%20I%20suggested%20we%20spend%20a%20year%20there%20and%20then%20reassess%20after%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20major%20hurdle%20we%20faced%20was%20finding%20a%20place%20to%20live.%20Though%20small%2C%20Bright%20is%20a%20popular%20tourist%20destination%20known%20for%20its%20wineries%2C%20hiking%2C%20and%20gold%20rush%20history.%20It's%20surrounded%20by%20beautiful%20mountains%20and%20is%20a%20short%20dr