%20later%20this%20year%20if%20it%20wants%20a%20%26quot%3Bjungle%20raj%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20term%20frequently%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20JDU%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20RJD%20rule%20in%20Bihar%20--%20or%20a%20government%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20that%20focuses%20on%20development.%20%26quot%3BBihar%20has%20to%20decide%20if%20it%20wants%20Lalu-Rabri's%20jungle%20raj%20or%20the%20development%20path%20of%20Modiji%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20What%20the%20Congress%20could%20not%20do%20in%2065%20years%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20did%20in%2010%20years.%20Please%20vote%20in%20an%20NDA%20government%20again.%20We%20will%20make%20Bihar%20flood-free%20within%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Bihar%20in%202000%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20alliance%20has%20ruled%20Bihar%20for%20two%20decades.%20In%20the%20last%2025%20years%2C%20there%20have%20been%20two%20occasions%20when%20Nitish%20Kumar%20switched%20to%20the%20Opposition%20camp%20and%20ran%20the%20state%20government%20in%20alliance%20with%20RJD.%20Mr%20Kumar%20is%20now%20back%20in%20the%20NDA%20camp%20and%20is%20prepping%20with%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20Bihar%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20his%20family%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLalu-Rabri%20regime%20here%20and%20Sonia-Manmohan%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20did%20nothing%20for%20Bihar.%20Lalu's%20two%20sons%20are%20now%20prepping%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%20His%20daughter%20(Misa%20Bharti)%20is%20in%20Parliament.%20His%20wife%20Rabri%20Devi%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20House%20(legislative%20council).%20Lalu%20is%20busy%20'setting'%20his%20family.%20He%20did%20not%20'set'%20the%20youngsters%20in%20Bihar.%20But%20Narendra%20Modi%20gave%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20ensured%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20grand%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20temple%20for%20Mata%20Janki%20--%20an%20epithet%20used%20for%20Sita%20--%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20has%20encouraged%20holidays%20for%20the%20Chhath%20festival.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20has%20allocated%20Rs%209%20lakh%20crore%20for%20Bihar's%20development.%20Thirteen%20greenfield%20expressways%20are%20being%20built.%20We%20will%20build%20seven%20bridges%20with%20an%20outlay%20of%20Rs%208%2C000%20crore.%20The%20Centre%20also%20set%20up%20a%20makhana%20board%20in%20Bihar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20listing%20the%20Budget%20announcements%20for%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20was%20a%20big%20winner%20in%20this%20Budget%2C%20with%20the%20government%20making%20key%20announcements%20for%20the%20state.%20The%20announcements%20were%20seen%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20upcoming%20state%20polls%20and%20JDU's%20critical%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%20after%20it%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20general%20election%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20RJD%20spokesperson%20Shakti%20Yadav%20called%20him%20the%20%26quot%3Bhero%20of%20Gujarat's%20jungleraj%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BFor%2020%20years%2C%20Bihar%20has%20had%20a%20JDU-BJP%20government.%20The%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20is%20deplorable.%20We%20want%20to%20know%20what%20work%20the%20BJP%20has%20done%20for%20Bihar's%20development.%20Bihar%20has%20failed%20in%20terms%20of%20education%2C%20per%20capita%20income%20and%20investment.%20And%20we%20are%20at%20the%20top%20in%20migration%20for%20work.%20NDA%20has%20done%20nothing%20other%20than%20looting%20Bihar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%20know%20everything%20and%20they%20have%20made%20up%20their%20minds%20to