%20already%20set%20up%20529%20accounts%20for%20his%20two%20kids%2C%20who%20are%20both%20under%2010.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Bank%20of%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERobert%20Furst%20is%20a%20wealth%20advisor%20at%20Merrill%20Lynch%20and%20the%20father%20to%20a%20four%20and%20six%20year%20old.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFurst%20said%20investing%20and%20charitable%20giving%20are%20core%20habits%20he%20wants%20to%20instill%20in%20his%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20has%20also%20set%20up%20529%20plans%20for%20each%20child%20and%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20live%20frugally%20to%20build%20wealth.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%2038-year-old%20Robert%20Furst%2C%20a%20senior%20VP%20at%20Merrill%20Lynch%2C%20a%20wealth%20management%20division%20of%20the%20Bank%20of%20America.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20really%20fortunate%20to%20have%20amazing%20role%20models%20in%20my%20life%2C%20and%20I'm%20very%20intentional%20about%20being%20a%20role%20model%20for%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20joined%20Merrill%20Lynch%20in%202013.%20I%20provide%20wealth%20management%20advice%20to%20our%20clients%2C%20who%20include%20business%20owners%2C%20professional%20athletes%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20lawyers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20my%20job%2C%20I've%20focused%20a%20lot%20on%20educating%20the%20next%20generation%20about%20finances.%20It's%20given%20me%20a%20cheat%20code%20for%20dealing%20with%20my%20own%20kids%2C%20who%20are%20six%20and%20four.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20ways%20I've%20decided%20to%20teach%20my%20kids%20about%20financial%20literacy%20and%20how%20I'm%20planning%20ahead%20to%20set%20them%20up%20for%20financial%20success.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a20c6e32-544c-404e-bef3-766918ee4d53%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EEncouraging%20charitable%20giving%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20think%20my%20children%20are%20too%20young%20to%20learn%20about%20gratitude%2C%20compassion%2C%20and%20appreciation.%20If%20we%20start%20those%20habits%20early%2C%20they%20will%20stay%20with%20them%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20kids%20save%20money%20in%20piggy%20banks%20for%20charitable%20giving.%20When%20they've%20accumulated%20enough%20funds%2C%20they'll%20choose%2C%20with%20a%20little%20guidance%2C%20where%20to%20donate%20those%20funds.%20At%20four%20and%20six%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20want%20our%20kids%20to%20focus%20on%20saving%20for%20charities%20and%20helping%20the%20less%20fortunate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20my%20six%20year%20old%20turns%20seven%20and%20starts%20first%20grade%2C%20I'll%20introduce%20him%20to%20investing%20and%20we%20will%20explore%20what%20stocks%20he%20would%20want%20to%20create%20his%20first%20portfolio.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20kids%20have%20a%20head%20start%20in%20life%20with%20two%20loving%20parents%20with%20good%20jobs.%20We've%20already%20started%20putting%20money%20away%20for%20college.%20I%20want%20to%20teach%20them%20that%20once%20a%20family%20has%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3Eenough%26quot%3B%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20give%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225afcd3ca-2981-4f52-94c6-27f7f0ce988d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ELetting%20them%20try%20out%20investing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20dad%20worked%20in%20finance%20and%20would%20cut%20articles%20out%20of%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20for%20me%20to%20read.%20He%20treated%20me%20like%20his%20%26quot%3Bjunior%20partner%26quot%3B%20and%20talked%20to%20me%20about%20business%20decisions%20he%20made%20at%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20got%20birthday%20money%20as%20a%20kid%2C%20I%20told%20my%20dad%20I%20wanted%20to%20invest%20it.%20He%20let%20me%20and%20this%20spurred%20my%20interest%20in%20the%20market.%20I%20saw%20the%20power%20of%20making%20a%20good%20investment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20planning%20to%20introduce%20my%20oldest%20child%20to%20investing%20soon.%20I%20want%20him%20to%20use%20his%20money%20to%20pick%20some%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%2C%20so%20he%20can%20feel%20the%20impact%20of%20decisions%20he%20makes.%20Nowadays%2C%20it's%20relatively%20easy%20to%20open%20a%20Uniform%20Transfers%20to%20Minors%20Act%20(UTMA)%20account%20and%20let%20my%20children%20pick%20some%20stocks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20investment%20coaching%20with%20the%20children%20of%20our%20clients.%20Once%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20visited%20our%20office.%20We%20pulled%20the%20research%20reports%20for%20companies%20he'd%20picked%20and%20discussed%20what%20can%20indicate%20an%20advisable%20or%20ill-advised%20investment.%20By%20pulling%20research%20reports%20of%20companies%20he%20selected%2C%20the%20child%20felt%20heard%20and%20respected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20child%20learned%20financial%20terms%20associated%20with%20stock%20research%2C%20so%20next%20time%20he%20wants%20to%20do%20some%20digging%2C%20jargon%20will%20not%20be%20a%20barrier%20to%20entry.%20I%20absolutely%20intend%20to%20do%20this%20with%20my%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20not%20about%20getting%20kids%20to%20have%20amazing%20returns.%20It's%20about%20getting%20them%20engaged.%20If%20they%20invest%20for%20long%20enough%2C%20they%20can%20also%20see%20the%20power%20of%20compounding.%20Time%20in%20the%20market%20beats%20timing%20the%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bbeefc78-4a29-4f93-a805-befe1bd9e6b9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ETeaching%20them%20the%20value%20of%20hard%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20once%20asked%20my%20parents%20for%20a%20video%20game%20system%2C%20and%20my%20mom%20told%20me%20she%20wouldn't%20pay%20for%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20ended%20up%20working%20in%20a%20friend%20of%20my%20dad's%20factory%20doing%20simple%20jobs%20like%20packing%20boxes.%20Soon%2C%20I%20had%20enough%20money%20to%20buy%20myself%20the%20game%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20won't%20have%20my%20kids%20working%20in%20factories%2C%20but%20they%20do%20know%20that%20their%20parents%20value%20hard%20work.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESometimes%2C%20my%20children%20will%20ask%20why%20my%20wife%20or%20I%20have%20to%20work%20late.%20We%20let%20them%20know%20that%20we%20strive%20to%20provide%20a%20good%20life%20for%20the%20family%20and%20that%20we%20work%20hard%20to%20earn%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20food%2C%20our%20home%2C%20and%20their%20education.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20want%20them%20to%20know%20that%20nothing%20is%20guaranteed%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20intend%20to%20pay%20them%20for%20chores.%20It%20could%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20making%20their%20beds.%20That's%20not%20a%20high-value%20item%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20something%20to%20me%20if%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291fbd6eb-5bcb-4b61-972e-73dcf56ba7cf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaving%20for%20their%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20my%20financial%20goals%20is%20to%20send%20both%20of%20my%20kids%20to%20college%20debt-free%2C%20so%20I%20set%20up%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-529-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E529%20plan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20had%20Social%20Security%20numbers.%20A%20529%20is%20a%20tax-advantaged%20education%20investment%20account%20that%20can%20help%20a%20child%20to%20attend%20college%20without%20incurring%20debt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20child%20has%20their%20own%20529.%20This%20is%20important%20because%20my%20children%20are%20of%20different%20ages%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3EI'll%20invest%20in%20their%20529s%20in%20line%20with%20when%20they%20go%20to%20college%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20we%20get%20closer%20to%20college%2C%20we'll%20lessen%20the%20risk%20level%20because%20the%20money%20will%20need%20to%20be%20spent%20sooner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20also%20want%20to%20accumulate%20enough%20wealth%20to%20give%20my%20children%20choices%20in%20life.%20If%20one%20wants%20to%20work%20in%20finance%20or%20tech%2C%20they%20may%20not%20need%20help%20from%20my%20wife%20and%20me.%20But%20if%20one%20of%20them%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20social%20worker%2C%20the%20financial%20rewards%20might%20look%20a%20little%20different.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20want%20my%20kids%20to%20be%20held%20back%20from%20doing%20amazing%20work%20in%20the%20community%20for%20financial%20reasons.%20We%20want%20to%20support%20them%20so%20they%20can%20make%20that%20choice%20without%20worrying%20about%20the%20salary%20difference.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20families%20I%20have%20counseled%20help%20subsidize%20a%20child%20who%20worked%20diligently%20in%20a%20less%20lucrative%20career%2C%20and%20this%20is%20something%20I%20admired.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe're%20planning%20for%20this%20by%20setting%20money%20aside%20and%20only%20buying%20what%20we%20need.%20We%20can%20afford%20to%20buy%20more%20luxury%20goods%20than%20we%20do%2C%20and%20that's%20by%20design.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'll%20probably%20tell%20my%20kids%20that%20we've%20got%20this%20money%20set%20aside%20for%20them%20when%20they're%20around%20college%20age.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20tell%20them%20too%20early%20as%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20them%20to%20rely%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20yo