y-heloc-housing-market-consumer-spending-recession-real-estate-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pandemic-era%20housing%20boom%20swelled%20Americans'%20home%20equity%20to%20record%20levels.%20Tapping%20into%20that%20could%20prop%20up%20the%20consumer%20and%20the%20economy%20in%20a%20slowdown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40businessinsider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-equity-heloc-housing-market-consumer-spending-recession-real-estate-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Connection%20Emerges%20In%20Bangkok%20Skyscraper%20That%20Collapsed%20During%20Quake%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Chinese-backed%20construction%20firm%20is%20being%20investigated%20over%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%2033-storey%20high-rise%20in%20Thailand's%20Bangkok%20during%20Friday's%207.7-magnitude%20earthquake%20that%20struck%20central%20Myanmar.%20The%20unfinished%20building%20crumbled%20in%20seconds%2C%20sending%20a%20cloud%20of%20dust%20and%20debris%20into%20the%20air%20and%20trapping%20dozens%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20AFP%2C%20as%20of%20Sunday%2C%2017%20deaths%20have%20been%20confirmed%2C%20with%2032%20injured%20and%2083%20still%20unaccounted%20for%20-%20most%20of%20them%20construction%20workers%20from%20the%20site%20of%20the%20collapsed%20building.%20Search%20and%20rescue%20teams%20continue%20working%20under%20intense%20heat%20to%20locate%20possible%20survivors.%20Thermal%20imaging%20drones%20have%20detected%20at%20least%2015%20people%20who%20may%20still%20be%20alive.%20Eight%20bodies%20have%20been%20pulled%20from%20the%20debris%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Bangkok's%20skyline%20being%20filled%20with%20high-rise%20buildings%20under%20construction%2C%20no%20other%20projects%20suffered%20similar%20destruction.%20Experts%20and%20officials%20are%20now%20questioning%20the%20structural%20integrity%20of%20the%20collapsed%20building%2C%20which%20belonged%20to%20Thailand's%20State%20Audit%20Office%20(SAO)%20and%20had%20been%20under%20construction%20for%20three%20years%20at%20a%20reported%20cost%20of%20over%20two%20billion%20baht%20(45%20million%20pounds).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThailand's%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Anutin%20Charnvirakul%20has%20ordered%20an%20urgent%20investigation%2C%20giving%20an%20expert%20panel%20seven%20days%20to%20determine%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fworld-news%2F2025%2F03%2F29%2Fchinese-firm-investigated-bangkok-skyscraper-quake-collapse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20the%20UK's%20Telegraph%2C%20the%20SAO%20building%20was%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20Italian-Thai%20Development%20Plc%20(ITD)%20and%20China%20Railway%20Number%2010%20(Thailand)%20Ltd.%20The%20latter%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20China%20Railway%20Number%2010%20Engineering%20Group%20Company%2C%20which%20holds%20a%2049%20per%20cent%20stake%20-%20the%20maximum%20foreign%20ownership%20allowed%20under%20Thai%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20Railway%20Number%2010%20Thailand%2C%20established%20in%202018%2C%20has%20operated%20as%20a%20contractor%20for%20large%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20including%20office%20buildings%2C%20railways%2C%20and%20public%20roads%2C%20the%20report%20claimed.%20The%20company%20reported%20a%20net%20loss%20of%20199.66%20million%20baht%20in%202023%2C%20with%20revenue%20of%20206.25%20million%20baht%20and%20expenses%20of%20354.95%20million%20baht.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20Thai%20shareholders%20include%3A%20Sophon%20Meechai%20(40.80%25)%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20stakes%20in%20five%20other%20companies%3B%20Prachuab%20Sirikhet%20(10.20%25)%2C%20with%20investments%20in%20six%20companies%3B%20Manas%20Sri-anant%20(less%20than%201%25)%2C%20who%20holds%20shares%20in%20ten%20other%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20Bangkok%2C%20the%20earthquake%20caused%20devastation%20across%20Myanmar%2C%20where%20over%201%2C600%20people%20have%20been%20confirmed%20dead%2C%20and%20thousands%20more%20injured.%20The%20tremors%2C%20which%20originated%20northwest%20of%20Sagaing%2C%20demolished%20buildings%20and%20infrastructure%20across%20Mandalay%2C%20one%20of%20Myanmar's%20largest%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMyanmar's%20junta%20leader%2C%20Min%20Aung%20Hlaing%2C%20issued%20a%20rare%20international%20plea%20for%20aid%2C%20a%20stark%20departure%20from%20the%20regime's%20usual%20stance%20of%20rejecting%20foreign%20assistance.%20The%20country%20has%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20across%20six%20regions%2C%20and%20hospitals%20are%20overwhelmed%20with%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Thailand%2C%20the%20earthquake%20forced%20the%20evacuation%20of%20hospitals%20and%20office%20towers.%20Even%20in%20areas%20where%20buildings%20remained%20standing%2C%20footage%20captured%20rooftop%20swimming%20pools%20spilling%20their%20water%20down%20high-rises%20as%20the%20tremors%20rippled%20through%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743323400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F953q23ho_bangkok-earthquake_625x300_28_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmyanmar-earthquake-thailand-earthquake-a-china-connection-in-bangkoks-33-storey-building-brought-down-by-quake-8045516%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Chinese-backed%20construction%20firm%20is%20being%20investigated%20over%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%2033-storey%20high-rise%20in%20Thailand's%20Bangkok%20during%20Friday's%207.7-magnitude%20earthquake%20that%20struck%20central%20Myanmar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmyanmar-earthquake-thailand-earthquake-a-china-connection-in-bangkoks-33-storey-building-brought-down-by-quake-8045516%