ope%20the%20slower%20Guwahati%20pitch%20benefits%20their%20spin%20attack.%20Weather%20is%20predicted%20to%20be%20warm%20and%20pleasant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMust%20Ensure%20Movies%20Don't%20Spread%20Hatred%26quot%3B%3A%20Mohanlal's%20Apology%20After%20Uproar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%20surrounding%20his%20latest%20movie%20L2%20Empuraan%2C%20superstar%20Mohanlal%20has%20issued%20an%20apology%20and%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bregrets%20the%20pain%20caused%26quot%3B%20to%20his%20loved%20fans.%20The%20actor%20added%20that%20the%20movie's%20production%20team%20had%20decided%20to%20remove%20some%20mentions%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20an%20uproar%20over%20some%20references%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20riots.%20Actor-filmmaker%20Prithviraj%20Sukumaran%2C%20who%20has%20directed%20the%20movie%2C%20has%20shared%20Mohanlal's%20Facebook%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20learnt%20that%20some%20of%20the%20political-social%20themes%20that%20have%20emerged%20in%20the%20expression%20of%20the%20movie%20'Empuraan'%2C%20the%20second%20part%20of%20the%20'Lucifer'%20franchise%2C%20have%20caused%20a%20lot%20of%20disappointment%20to%20many%20of%20my%20lovers.%20As%20an%20artist%2C%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20ensure%20that%20none%20of%20my%20movies%20harbours%20hatred%20towards%20any%20political%20movement%2C%20idea%20or%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohanlal%20said%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20I%20and%20the%20Empuraan%20team%20sincerely%20regret%20the%20mental%20pain%20caused%20to%20my%20loved%20ones%2C%20and%20with%20the%20realisation%20that%20the%20responsibility%20lies%20with%20all%20of%20us%20who%20worked%20behind%20the%20film%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20together%20to%20compulsorily%20remove%20such%20parts%20from%20the%20movie%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20lived%20my%20cinematic%20life%20as%20one%20of%20you%20for%20the%20last%20four%20decades.%20Your%20love%20and%20faith%20are%20my%20only%20strength.%20I%20believe%20Mohanlal%20is%20not%20greater%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2064-year-old%20actor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20film's%20producer%20Gokulam%20Gopalan%20had%20said%20the%20production%20team%20had%20decided%20on%2017%20cuts%20in%20the%20movie%20and%20its%20new%20version%20will%20release%20in%20theatres%20next%20week.%20Some%20scenes%20depicting%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20riots%20would%20be%20cut%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20antagonist%20Baba%20Bajrangi%20will%20be%20changed%20and%20certain%20dialogues%20will%20be%20muted%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gopalan%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20film%20had%20cleared%20the%20Censor%20but%20the%20cuts%20would%20be%20made%20so%20that%20the%20sentiments%20of%20a%20section%20of%20people%20would%20not%20be%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20drawing%20huge%20crowds%20and%20has%20crossed%20the%20Rs%20100-crore%20milestone%20at%20the%20box%20office%20globally%20in%20just%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20references%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20riots%20have%20sparked%20a%20massive%20political%20row%2C%20with%20social%20media%20users%20hitting%20out%20at%20Mohanlal%20and%20Prithviraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20not%20launched%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20movie%2C%20but%20state%20party%20chief%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20has%20said%20he%20was%20disappointed%20and%20that%20he%20would%20not%20watch%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20movie%20should%20be%20watched%20as%20a%20movie.%20it%20can't%20be%20seen%20as%20history.%20Also%2C%20any%20movie%20that%20tries%20to%20build%20a%20story%20by%20distorting%20the%20truth%20is%20doomed%20to%20fail.%20So%2C%20will%20I%20watch%20this%20sequel%20to%20Lucifer%3F%20No.%20Am%20I%20disappointed%20by%20this%20type%20of%20moviemaking%3F%20-%20Yes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Ganesh%2C%20state%20general%20secretary%20of%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Yuva%20Morcha%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20Prithviraj%20and%20demanded%20an%20investigation%20into%20his%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20connections%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20Prithviraj's%20moves%20follow%20an%20'anti-national'%20pattern%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20ideological%20parent%20RSS%20published%20in%20its%20mouthpiece%20Organiser%20an%20article%20criticising%20L2%20Empuraan%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisturbing%2C%20divisive%20tale%20disguised%20as%20cinema%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20backed%20the%20movie%20and%20said%20the%20criticism%20showed%20the%20%26quot%3Bintolerance%26quot%3B%20of%20Sangh%20Parivar.%20He%20said%20movies%20such%20as%20'The%20Accidental%20Prime%20Minister'%20and%20'Emergency'%20were%20critical%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20had%20welcomed%20them.%20Movies%2C%20the%20Congress%20veteran%20said%2C%20always%20discuss%20politics.%20%26quot%3BThat%20will%20be%20favourable%20for%20a%20section%20and%20against%20some%20others.%20These%20are%20all%20part%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression.%20The%20BJP%20should%20introspect%20whether%20it%20is%20right%20to%20show%20intolerance%20only%20when%20they%20are%20criticised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20CPM%20leader%20and%20Kerala%20minister%20V%20Sivankutty%20said%20the%202002%20riots%20were%20part%20of%20Indian%20history%20and%20generations%20would%20know%20about%20it%20even%20if%20%26quot%3Bscissors%20are%20used%26quot%3B%20to%20cut%20scenes.%20%26quot%3BFreedom%20of%20expression%20is%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20democracy.%20Any%20action%20to%20prevent%20it%20should%20be%20opposed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743322140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fk79t1ra_mohanlal-l2-empuraan_650