Prime%20Minister%20Mark%20Carney%20faces%20allegations%20of%20plagiarism%20in%20his%201995%20doctoral%20thesis%20at%20Oxford%20University%2C%20with%20experts%20identifying%20at%20least%2010%20potential%20instances.%20The%20timing%20of%20these%20claims%2C%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20Canadian%20election%2C%20could%20jeopardize%20his%20campaign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmark-carney-faces-plagiarism-allegations-over-oxford-thesis-ahead-of-canada-fed-elections%2Farticleshow%2F119745482.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmark-carney-faces-plagiarism-allegations-over-oxford-thesis-ahead-of-canada-fed-elections%2Famp_articleshow%2F119745482.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmark-carney-faces-plagiarism-allegations-over-oxford-thesis-ahead-of-canada-fed-elections%2Famp_articleshow%2F119745482.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chirag%20Paswan%20Asked%20About%20His%20Take%20On%20Namaz%20On%20Streets.%20What%20BJP%20Ally%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20push%20against%20Muslims%20offering%20namaz%20on%20streets%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20ally%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20said%20these%20are%20%26quot%3Buseless%20subjects%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20country%20faces%20several%20other%20major%20issues%20that%20need%20to%20be%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Times%20Now%20event%2C%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20leader%20was%20asked%20about%20his%20take%20on%20the%20opposition%20to%20namaz%20on%20the%20streets.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20faltu%20(useless)%20talk.%20This%20should%20not%20even%20be%20discussed%2C%20it%20is%20meaningless.%20There%20are%20major%20issues%20in%20the%20country%20that%20we%20need%20to%20discuss.%20The%20problem%20is%20when%20we%20start%20talking%20about%20these%20irrelevant%20topics%2C%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20tension%20is%20created%20in%20the%20society%20and%20the%20country.%20Without%20any%20reason%2C%20rifts%20are%20created%20between%20communities%20and%20people.%20This%20is%20meaningless%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Paswan%20said%20people%20have%20been%20offering%20namaz%20on%20the%20streets%20for%20years.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20were%20not%20talking%20about%20this%2C%20you%20would%20possibly%20be%20asking%20about%20what%20work%20I%20did%20as%20Food%20Processing%20minister.%20But%20these%20things%20would%20become%20secondary%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%20that%20people%20in%20BJP%2C%20his%20ally%2C%20were%20talking%20about%20this%2C%20the%20minister%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20agree.%20That's%20what%20I%20am%20saying.%20I%20am%20an%20educated%20youth%20from%20the%2021st%20Century.%20We%20should%20not%20interfere%20in%20religious%20matters.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20faith.%20I%20threw%20an%20Iftaar%20party%20and%20I%20went%20there%20with%20a%20tilak.%20It%20is%20my%20faith.%20I%20won't%20forget%20my%20religious%20values%20to%20respect%20your%20religion%2C%20but%20these%20are%20issues%20behind%20closed%20doors.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20faith.%20Some%20people%20follow%20a%20faith%2C%20others%20don't.%20Many%20Hindus%20don't%20have%20a%20tilak.%20Are%20they%20not%20Hindus%3F%20This%20is%20personal%20faith.%20Why%20are%20attempts%20being%20made%20to%20generalise%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20also%20talking%20about%20my%20allies.%20If%20you%20are%20saying%20they%20are%20doing%20it%2C%20I%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20politics.%20I%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20bigger%20things%20that%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20rather%20than%20talking%20about%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Paswan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamaz%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20other%20public%20places%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20political%20issue%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20While%20one%20section%20opposes%20this%20and%20says%20religious%20customs%20should%20not%20be%20done%20in%20public%20places%2C%20others%20argue%20that%20one%20should%20not%20create%20an%20issue%20out%20of%20this%20unless%20such%20acts%20inconvenience%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20late%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20come%20under%20the%20spotlight%20after%20district%20administrations%20in%20some%20part%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20adopted%20a%20strict%20approach%20against%20allowing%20namaz%20on%20the%20streets%20during%20Eid.%20This%20also%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Muslim%20organisations%20opposing%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20brought%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20district%20administration's%20push%20against%20namaz%20on%20streets%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20MP%20Ravi%20Kishan%20said%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20must%20celebrate%20festivals%20without%20troubling%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20Hindus%20as%20well%20as%20Muslims%2C%20celebrate%20your%20festivals%20without%20troubling%20the%20public.%20All%20the%20scholars%20and%20Maulanas%20say%20that%20Namaz%20is%20accepted%20in%20the%20mosque.%20Who%20started%20this%20practice%20on%20the%20streets%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kishan%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20MP%20Husain%20Dalwai%20has%20criticised%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government's%20stand%20on%20namaz%20on%20streets%20and%20alleged%20it%20reflects%20%26quot%3Bunderlying%20hatred%26quot%3B%20towards%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Eid%2C%20Muslims%20traditionally%20go%20to%20mosques%20to%20offer%20'namaz'%2C%20but%20due%20to%20limited%20space%2C%20many%20pray%20on%20the%20roads.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%2C%20do%20only%20Muslims%20pray%20on%20th