the%20self-proclaimed%20godman%20has%20been%20travelling%20from%20Jodhpur%20to%20Indore%2C%20Ujjain%20and%20Surat%2C%20and%20meeting%20his%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20kind%20of%20illness%20does%20he%20have%3F%20Now%20the%20danger%20to%20our%20family%20has%20increased.%20He%20can%20do%20anything%20to%20us%20at%20any%20time.%20Now%20we%20are%20only%20dependent%20on%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20Rajesh%20Dwivedi%20said%20a%20guard%20has%20been%20deployed%20at%20the%20rape%20survivor's%20house%20and%20two%20gunmen%20have%20also%20been%20given%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20a%20CCTV%20camera%2C%20covering%20the%20survivor's%20entire%20house%2C%20has%20been%20installed%20in%20front%20of%20her%20residence.%20The%20local%20Kotwali%20police%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20monitor%20her%20house%20while%20patrolling%20at%20night%2C%20the%20SP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20officers%20are%20constantly%20monitoring%20the%20security%20of%20the%20survivor's%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsaram%20was%20convicted%20in%20the%20rape%20case%20in%202018%20and%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20he%20was%20convicted%20by%20a%20Gujarat%20court%20for%20raping%20a%20woman%20disciple%20at%20his%20ashram%20in%20the%20Motera%20area%20of%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743318840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fitn6b7k8_asaram-bapu-bail_625x300_28_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhe-can-do-anything-to-us-rape-survivors-father-on-fresh-bail-for-asa