agic%20incident%2C%20and%20medical%20aid%20and%20compensation%20for%20victims'%20families%20are%20being%20arranged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-kills-own-civilians-during-military-operation-admits-unintended-consequences%2Farticleshow%2F119742670.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-kills-own-civilians-during-military-operation-admits-unintended-consequences%2Famp_articleshow%2F119742670.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-kills-own-civilians-during-military-operation-admits-unintended-consequences%2Famp_articleshow%2F119742670.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Sujata%20Karthikeyan%2C%20Top%20Odisha%20IAS%20Officer%20Who%20Got%20Early%20Retirement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESenior%20Odisha%20cadre%20IAS%20officer%20Sujata%20Karthikeyan%20has%20taken%20voluntary%20retirement%2C%20after%20the%20Centre%20approved%20her%20application%2C%20instructing%20the%20Odisha%20government%20to%20issue%20the%20necessary%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2013%2C%202025%2C%20the%20Central%20Government%20officially%20approved%20her%20request%20for%20voluntary%20retirement%2C%20waiving%20the%20mandatory%20three-month%20notice%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Sujata%20Karthikeyan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Karthikeyan%2C%20a%202000-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20graduated%20in%20Political%20Science%20from%20Lady%20Shri%20Ram%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University.%20She%20later%20obtained%20a%20Master's%20Degree%20in%20International%20Politics%20from%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Karthikeyan's%20career%20began%20in%20the%20Maoist-affected%20Sundargarh%20district%20of%20Odisha%2C%20where%20she%20spearheaded%20several%20social%20initiatives.%20In%202005%2C%20she%20launched%20a%20bicycle%20distribution%20scheme%20for%20high%20school%20girls%20under%20the%20motto%20'Mobility%20is%20Empowerment.'%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202006%2C%20she%20introduced%20eggs%20into%20the%20Mid-Day%20Meal%20(MDM)%20scheme%20in%20Sundargarh.%20Instead%20of%20increasing%20dal%20or%20oil%20quantities%2C%20eggs%20were%20added%20to%20students'%20meals.%20This%20initiative%20was%20later%20scaled%20up%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Karthikeyan%20was%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BFootball%20Collector%26quot%3B%20in%20Sundargarh.%20She%20promoted%20sports%2C%20particularly%20football%20and%20hockey%2C%20among%20youth%20in%20Maoist-prone%20areas%2C%20distributing%20equipment%20and%20setting%20up%20hostels%20for%20aspiring%20athletes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20Ms%20Karthikeyan's%20most%20notable%20contributions%20was%20her%20leadership%20of%20'Mission%20Shakti%2C'%20Odisha's%20flagship%20women's%20empowerment%20programme.%20Under%20her%20guidance%2C%20the%20programme%20grew%20to%20support%2070%20lakh%20women%2C%20with%20credit%20linkages%20for%20women's%20self-help%20groups%20(SHGs)%20increasing%20from%20Rs%20500%20crore%20to%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%20over%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20the%20first%20woman%20Collector%20of%20Cuttack%20district%20%2C%20Ms%20Karthikeyan%20launched%20the%20'Mamta'%20scheme%2C%20a%20conditional%20cash%20transfer%20programme%20for%20pregnant%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDuring%20her%20brief%20tenure%20as%20Secretary%20of%20Culture%2C%20Ms%20Karthikeyan%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20organising%20the%20first%20World%20Odia%20Language%20Conference%20in%20Bhubaneswar.%20T%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBefore%20her%20retirement%2C%20Ms%20Karthikeyan%20served%20as%20Special%20Secretary%20in%20Odisha's%20Finance%20Department.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20May%202024%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20ordered%20Ms%20Karthikeyan's%20transfer%20from%20her%20role%20as%20Commissioner-cum-Secretary%20of%20Mission%20Shakti%2C%20citing%20allegations%20of%20office%20misuse.%20Following%20the%20BJD's%20defeat%2C%20she%20took%20six%20months%20of%20leave%2C%20which%20was%20later%20denied%20an%20extension%20by%20the%20state's%20BJP-led%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20is%20marred%20to%20VK%20Pandian%2C%20a%20former%20bureaucrat-turned-politician%20and%20close%20aide%20of%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik.%20Mr%20Pandian%20also%20took%20voluntary%20retirement%20in%202023%20to%20join%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD).%20He%20later%20withdrew%20from%20active%20politics%20following%20the%20BJD's%20electoral%20defeat%20in%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743313140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ftrfl5kg8_sujata-karthikeyan-_625x300_30_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsujata-karthikeyan-vk-pandian-who-is-sujata-karthikeyan-top-odisha-ias-officer-who-got-early-retirement-8044777%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20Odisha%20cadre%20IAS%20officer%20Sujata%20Karthikeyan%20has%20taken%20voluntary%20retirement%2C%20after%20the%20Centre%20approved%20her%20application%2C%20instructing%20the%20Odisha%20government%20to%20issue%20the%20necessary%20notification.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsujata-karthikeyan-vk-pandian-who-is-sujata-karthikeyan-top-odisha-ias-officer-who-got-early-retirement-8044777%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20GDP%20growth%20projected%20at%206.4%25%20for%20FY25%2C%206.5%25%20for%20FY26%3A%20EY%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743312895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-gdp-growth-projec