%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20aspects%20of%20this%20approach%20is%20something%20called%20%E2%80%98deep%20listening%E2%80%99.%20This%20means%20immersing%20fully%20in%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20world%20%E2%80%94%20understanding%20their%20culture%2C%20challenges%2C%20and%20aspirations%20%E2%80%94%20while%20making%20careful%20observations.%20The%20programme%20combines%20deep%20listening%20with%20steps%20like%20%E2%80%9Cco-creation%E2%80%9D%2C%20where%20solutions%20are%20developed%20together%20with%20the%20participants%2C%20%E2%80%9Cprototyping%E2%80%9D%20to%20test%20ideas%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cacceleration%E2%80%9D%20to%20bring%20these%20ideas%20to%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FInclusive-entrepreneurship-2-1743071716.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Community%20listening%20session%20with%20a%20CLF%20in%20Ghuguwa%2C%20Jhansi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20using%20a%20specifically%20designed%20snake%20and%20ladder%20game.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FInclusive-entrepreneurship-2-1743071716.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FInclusive-entrepreneurship-2-1743071716-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FInclusive-entrepreneurship-2-1743071716-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FInclusive-entrepreneurship-2-1743071716-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FInclusive-entrepreneurship-2-1743071716-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-416303%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECommunity%20listening%20sessio